Her life is but a fleeting rain.
<br>
Steel is her body, and rain is her namesake.
<br>
The passing rain as myriad tears of the sky.
<br>
Unknown to distinguishment, nor known in passing.
<br>
Have accumulated myriads of experience to overcome the trials.
<br>
On this fateful day, let the gathering of rain fell from heaven to the earth.
<br>
And let the passing shower be reborn as one held the dearest.
